Paintable is a jQuery plugin that makes any HTML canvas element paintable

Usage
Include paintable.js using
    <script src="http://www.golfsinteppadon.com/paintable.js"></script>
Call paintable
    $('#canvas').paintable();

Initializing paintable creates a paintable canvas, allowing users to draw on it. To use other tools, call methods to change tools and colors

Methods
.paintable('setTool', toolName)

toolName possibilities: "pencil", "eraser", "floodFill", "stamp"

.paintable('setColor', color)
.paintable('save')
.paintable('undo')